Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻过所有的杂志也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这摇头叹息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 与我相称的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.54,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都无法 讨得你的欢心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉让你失望了 说笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是与我紧紧地缠绕的话不行哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  别用那种冷冷的眼神望着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我照着自己的步调去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话我很快就会崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.59,0:22:38.57,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.10,0:22:44.27,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  这就是爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.52,0:22:49.69,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手寻找温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.82,0:22:55.57,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  奇迹也一定会发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.16,0:23:08.48,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有爱 就绝对有具体的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.00,0:23:19.51,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 现在 在我手中 有诞生的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.76,0:23:27.77,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神饱满  也不能   太过勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.15,0:23:33.07,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.51,0:23:44.18,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起来  培育茁壮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.94,0:00:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬间明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.84,0:00:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要开始就不会停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.63,0:00:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是深山的五重塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.66,0:00:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说力量的不可能犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.79,0:00:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.39,0:00:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.21,0:00:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.40,0:01:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的五重塔传说(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.12,0:01:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也该像这样出来走走才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.71,0:02:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏小兰姐姐参加杂志猜谜得了奖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.29,0:02:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过解开谜底的人不是柯南你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.42,0:02:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是简单得要死的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.48,0:02:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.99,0:02:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 这种沉闷的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.42,0:02:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就知道这种观光旅行一定没什么好看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.41,0:02:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.65,0:02:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始听到可以去旅行自己还高兴得不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.85,0:02:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你们两个去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.84,0:02:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回酒店去泡个澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.37,0:02:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 这里是禁烟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.71,0:02:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.71,0:02:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对旅行的人来讲这种地方的确很无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.13,0:02:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这种地方 我们在都市生活不常接触
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.06,0:02:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种可以清净心灵的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是难得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么年轻竟能讲出如此棒的话来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.83,0:03:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌弃的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我带你们到寺里面参观吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.05,0:03:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.97,0:03:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样很失礼啊 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.84,0:03:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.41,0:03:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座寺庙在四百年前修建完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经四百年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.58,0:03:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是古老啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.18,0:03:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是古老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.31,0:03:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它还见证着历史的种种变迁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.35,0:03:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如在五重塔旁边的草丛里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.85,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个从江户时代开始就一直使用的旧井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.66,0:03:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么现在不用了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它突然干枯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是一个失恋的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.37,0:03:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在井前哭了三天三夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.09,0:03:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些眼泪就和井水一起全部消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.21,0:03:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真荒谬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.38,0:04:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个五重塔有一个可怕的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.94,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么样的传说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在江户时代初期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持看中了一个年轻有为的青年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.84,0:04:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为他可以继任下一任的住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.58,0:04:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他爱上村长的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.18,0:04:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来他就触犯寺规和村长的女儿私奔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.60,0:04:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神明的老鹰将青年带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.24,0:04:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他吊在五重塔上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.39,0:04:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.65,0:04:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在江户时代中期的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.52,0:04:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个心术不正的住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将寺庙的贵重物品偷偷卖掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都沉溺于酒色之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天他突然失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.64,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了几天之后被发现吊死在五重塔的前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此之后大家就开始传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人触犯寺规就会受到五重塔的诅咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.32,0:05:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.48,0:05:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要露出这么可怕的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡…淡海大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.68,0:05:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是这个寺庙的住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.73,0:05:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.13,0:05:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次派大人带着小孩到底来这里做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.61,0:05:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们只是纯粹来观光的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑人物 不能相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让外面的人擅自进来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.21,0:05:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是观光是本寺的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这事整个寺庙被抢走了 难道你忘记了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.42,0:05:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那些人到最后必遭天谴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报应的天谴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.68,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.75,0:06:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是这座寺庙变成观光公司的物产了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.89,0:06:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备在附近建造一个主题公园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这一带就要改造了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持说是被他们骗了 一直在反对着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.67,0:06:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在他对观光客都是那种态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.63,0:06:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然胡乱吓人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.13,0:06:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要离开这个地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.53,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我爸爸很喜欢生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.91,0:06:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.81,0:06:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是我们这边不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父亲该不会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毛利小五郎先生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真是那个有名的名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我可以向我的孙子炫耀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.52,0:07:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还招待我们吃晚餐 实属荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.61,0:07:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倍感荣幸的应该是我们才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个酒店刚开业不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.46,0:07:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生这样的名人出现是个很好的宣传
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.44,0:07:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果自己可以派上用场的话我是很乐意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.06,0:07:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个酒店真是又豪华又漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还满意吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.16,0:07:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年这个时候我所推荐的主题公园就会完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.87,0:07:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候就会更好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.68,0:07:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这次工程花费不少吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.22,0:07:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多八十亿元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.06,0:07:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要完成之后 一年赚几百亿是不成问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记自我介绍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.27,0:08:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这家酒店的经理…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.72,0:08:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在这里丢人现眼了 尾村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.25,0:08:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且名侦探毛利先生来这里住宿的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.10,0:08:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要冈部讲才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.45,0:08:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的失职
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去给我反省一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.47,0:08:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你今晚不是要去东京吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在这里搭话真的好么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.99,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢慢享用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没用的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了 我太激动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是严格啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.74,0:08:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作方面的事情 不论什么 我都会毫不留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你领带夹上的是钻石吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.41,0:08:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这没什么大不了的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区五克拉而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有五克拉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 不要这样 很丢脸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.96,0:09:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.34,0:09:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是人类最真实的反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.51,0:09:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫做真实吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长 这是您要的雪茄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收据呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.93,0:09:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这样叫我怎么报销呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.92,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你一直都拿着这么多钱到处走吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 这只是一部分而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我讨厌用信用卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在这里悠闲地用餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是幻块寺的大公子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.42,0:09:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的修行已经结束了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.87,0:09:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用政治手段欺骗我父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为我会善罢甘休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.12,0:09:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是为此而回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等 请你不要讲出如此失礼的话来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我和你爸爸仔细商量过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.60,0:10:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.96,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让寺庙能继续经营
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.81,0:10:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说“暂时把寺庙的所有权交出来比较好办事”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我爸爸就这样相信了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.58,0:10:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我会遵循法律和你打官司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说的只有这些吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.30,0:10:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.88,0:10:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正在会客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有事的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天到我办公室来说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.24,0:10:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别以为我会就此放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.68,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.39,0:10:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂事不断 真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生和寺庙的人之间有什么过节吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些无聊的小问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.68,0:10:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们把这伟大的观光开发计划给想歪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.86,0:10:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我要把神圣的寺庙给毁掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一群无聊的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.86,0:10:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于观光的收入 那个寺庙也会因此得益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是些无知的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.84,0:11:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打那个寺庙歪主意的话会遭报应的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.96,0:11:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能说这种话啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那个寺庙的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.31,0:11:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也有不少人跑来劝过我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过正因为如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.72,0:11:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却觉得可以利用这来做招引客人的免费广告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是会做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.62,0:11:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 毛利侦探事务…所…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.32,0:11:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是冈部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天寺院的向导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.96,0:11:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报应真的应验了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你说遭报应了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.47,0:11:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请马上到寺庙这边来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 快点 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.91,0:12:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也稍微说明一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.02,0:12:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个很可怕的报应应验了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(诵经)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.12,0:12:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么报应嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.42,0:12:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是晨课而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.34,0:12:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.26,0:12:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.54,0:12:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报应！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鉴定方面的工作已经完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.95,0:13:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在准备要把遗体给取下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.91,0:13:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体是在五重塔的五楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在栏杆上绑上绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.13,0:13:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一边绕过屋顶的前端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.13,0:13:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后吊下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.16,0:13:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份应该是经营观光公司的小田英明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.68,0:13:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有个不认识的侦探正在上面确认情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探 是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.27,0:13:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 横沟刑事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.44,0:13:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是毛利先生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.49,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么会来这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.01,0:13:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为某些缘故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言归正传
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这个案件你有什么意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.83,0:13:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照情况来说应该是自杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.14,0:13:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然情况异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.04,0:13:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该没有他杀的可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此话怎讲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 小田先生拥有大约一百公斤的巨大体型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把他带到五楼上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.09,0:13:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通人是做不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.80,0:14:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算可以把他搬上去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楼梯通道也非常的狭窄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.18,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人要通过已经很不容易了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也有可能是拉上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过衣服就会被弄脏 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体也会有擦伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.73,0:14:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚去看过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有这些痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你已经调查到这种地步了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但话说回来 为什么会被吊在那里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点点…一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.71,0:14:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.86,0:14:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栏杆上有新的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绳子是新的却到处都有烧焦的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.24,0:14:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.62,0:14:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么让他下来好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚不着地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果脚踩不到栏杆的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小鬼 你怎么到这种地方来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.77,0:14:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.60,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找厕所结果迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来厕所并不在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.91,0:15:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 到底在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 那个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.35,0:15:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据鉴定报告来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.06,0:15:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五重塔里面没有什么灰尘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.11,0:15:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以无法确认有没有小田的脚印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有请这镇上的医生检查过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生并没有外伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为颈部受压迫而死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.08,0:15:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说颈部被勒是直接致死的原因了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.52,0:15:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推定死亡的时间是凌晨三点到四点之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.63,0:15:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田将酒店的总统套房当作自己的家在使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌晨两点左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.89,0:15:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总台的人看见他走了出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.37,0:15:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照时间来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.83,0:15:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能是直接到这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.93,0:15:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗书呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.38,0:15:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长 你为什么这么傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.79,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你稍微…稍微再等一下的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了 请问你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.34,0:16:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是0DA酒店的经理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫尾村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.46,0:16:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你好像不在这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.68,0:16:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 突然被派去出差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.42,0:16:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道一些关于他自杀的动机相关的头绪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.99,0:16:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去出差是为了筹募资金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这次失败的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.07,0:16:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本公司在这个月底就必须结业了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.51,0:16:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过社长他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我还要难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.46,0:16:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他昨天还带了一大笔现金呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长自尊心很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会让别人看到他的弱点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.20,0:16:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有时候还会死撑场面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.32,0:17:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺庙方面讲要寻求法律的手段来对付他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以社长很在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.02,0:17:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大叔的钱包不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.94,0:17:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱包？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.20,0:17:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随身物品中并没有钱包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.67,0:17:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不觉得奇怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生并没有换过衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天带的钱包竟然不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  既然要自杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.34,0:17:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还带那么多钱出来干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.99,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是常常叫你别在现场乱晃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.50,0:17:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个领带夹也不见了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.16,0:17:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.53,0:17:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.84,0:17:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以妨碍大人搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.24,0:17:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 关于领带夹是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生昨晚夹在领带上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.41,0:17:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个镶着华丽的五克拉钻石的领带夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的确没有看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.33,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说也有可能被抢劫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是遇到强盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.07,0:18:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是自己已经想自我了断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.11,0:18:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许就乖乖地把钱财给强盗了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.64,0:18:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 这根本不是被杀的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是被别人勒死的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.59,0:18:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被勒的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.84,0:18:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会因为很痛苦而用手去做拉扯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 手上并没有痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这真的是杀人案的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.23,0:18:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何将被害者吊到那么高的五重塔的前端呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.03,0:18:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了自杀之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能是人为的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.23,0:18:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算真的是有犯人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就是神明的报应了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.70,0:18:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是报应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.64,0:18:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对不敬之人的天谴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.58,0:18:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是静冈警局的横沟刑事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 你们是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.84,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是这个寺庙的住持 淡海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他的儿子 春海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.24,0:19:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这里的工作人员 冈部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.80,0:19:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位在凌晨三点到四点之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.41,0:19:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了些什么事情 可以告知吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.60,0:19:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是自杀的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.24,0:19:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 现在还不能下定论 而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.48,0:19:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生身上的财物可能被人拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.83,0:19:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道吃斋念佛的我们会去偷东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.56,0:19:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 为了参考我必须知道你们当时在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.28,0:19:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那件事情让我实在是很生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.67,0:19:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以当时我在大堂里面诵经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诵经…你在念经吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那种时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.77,0:19:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我预感到会有神明的报应出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.38,0:19:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报应…吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 春海先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.16,0:20:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在睡觉 五点钟起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后冈部就跑来通知我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.27,0:20:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田死了的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.14,0:20:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我非常惊讶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.53,0:20:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上给毛利先生打了电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.78,0:20:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不先打电话报警而是先打给毛利先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.07,0:20:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这家伙是小田的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.21,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他把小田介绍给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡…淡海大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是听信了小田社长的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.64,0:20:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果增加了观光游客 这里的香油钱也会增加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.16,0:20:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.17,0:20:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是被他给骗了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我“也”是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.46,0:20:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的住持好像被小田先生骗走了寺庙的所有权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.18,0:20:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你们三人都很恨小田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算恨他又怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.81,0:20:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边那位名侦探讲过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.56,0:20:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田除了自杀之外没有其他可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.26,0:20:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自杀的话不是没有犯人的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.86,0:20:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…还没有断定就是自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.39,0:21:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快点下个定论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.58,0:21:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想因为那肮脏的家伙把这神圣的地方给玷污了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.61,0:21:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.98,0:21:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生的钱包和领带夹都不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.34,0:21:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在这种状况来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.14,0:21:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了自杀之外别无它想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.98,0:21:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.82,0:21:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手肘的部位弄脏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.37,0:21:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是草的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是倒下去的时候擦到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.82,0:21:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双脚的后脚跟都沾有泥土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这里会有泥土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.19,0:21:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.07,0:21:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看上面烧焦的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.27,0:21:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.82,0:21:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.69,0:21:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是领带夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.77,0:21:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.09,0:22:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的案发现场就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.06,0:22:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的假设是正确的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生并不是自杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.10,0:22:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是他杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.37,0:22:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人大概就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.42,0:22:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候讲了那句话的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.38,0:22:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.20,0:23:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.62,0:23:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能站在栏杆上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.26,0:23:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么自杀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.56,0:23:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说是他杀的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.76,0:23:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离五十公分那么远的绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.93,0:24:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是怎么把它吊上去的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.93,0:24:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.59,0:24:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边是绑在栏杆上面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.38,0:24:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会打个活结呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.97,0:24:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.44,0:24:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的五重塔传说(后篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.03,0:24:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.63,0:24:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.28,0:24:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次是后篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.50,0:24:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说的真相可能更加恐怖哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.25,0:24:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
